description: Starts the specified WorkSpaces. You cannot start a WorkSpace unless it has a running mode of AutoStop or Manual and a state of STOPPED.

parameters.name: StartWorkspaceRequests
parameters.description: The WorkSpaces to start. You can specify up to 25 WorkSpaces. (dict) --- Information used to start a WorkSpace. WorkspaceId (string) --- The identifier of the WorkSpace.

nested_items.name: FailedRequests
nested_items.description: Information about the WorkSpaces that could not be started.

nested_items.name: ErrorCode
nested_items.description: The error code that is returned if the WorkSpace cannot be rebooted.

nested_items.name: ErrorMessage
nested_items.description: The text of the error message that is returned if the WorkSpace cannot be rebooted.
